Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.79,0:00:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚铃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米莉 艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.25,0:00:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 那是？
