Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷 明斯利是个什么样的地方知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.64,0:03:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说还原了地球过去的自然环境
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是最美丽的殖民卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.70,0:03:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没亲眼见过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.39,0:03:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旧国家战争结束后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是少数拒绝加入联邦的中立卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.58,0:03:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.61,0:03:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 被人围追堵截
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在明斯利集结兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:32.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备发动要塞攻略战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.64,0:03:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古鲁迪克舰长还真有胆识
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:38.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃尔夫中尉呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？ 刚才好像还在这里溜达呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:42.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.18,0:03:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢！小蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.78,0:03:56.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要这么叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:04:00.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉不去给机动战士维护下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.89,0:04:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从来都很相信工程师们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.71,0:04:07.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那些 太阳打西边出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然大驾光临这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:11.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想听下你的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的意见？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.09,0:04:15.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于这场战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我心里还是有犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.01,0:04:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样真的正确吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.72,0:04:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 你也会？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 你没有这种感觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问你也白问
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这船上谁不犹豫？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.63,0:04:35.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定是去送死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会犹豫才是正常人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.31,0:04:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:04:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备停靠明斯利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.89,0:05:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是集结地点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃伊诺基的旧友…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.85,0:05:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面乘这艘小船
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前往自然保护区内的巴明戈斯宅邸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里召开作战会议
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼 真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次身处这样的大自然中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.09,0:05:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人心情平静
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是明斯利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.18,0:05:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是中立卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不能保证没有敌人和联邦的眼线在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要放松警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前地球上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.15,0:05:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到处都是这样的风景啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.61,0:05:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太美了 没有比这里更适合我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.28,0:05:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 为了这次行动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.91,0:06:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅借给我们宅邸 还出资赞助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.14,0:06:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位巴明戈斯究竟是什么人物？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.71,0:06:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:09.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说是沃伊诺基的旧友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,值得信任吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,值不值得都得靠他了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:15.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船到桥头自然直
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.93,0:06:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古鲁迪克那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.62,0:06:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问什么AGE系统能不能加强歌姬号的战斗力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.52,0:06:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能这么用？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.29,0:06:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在明斯利只滞留两周 时间来得及吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AGE系统本是高达专用的进化系统
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.23,0:06:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战舰有没有福气用得上它是未知数
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.99,0:06:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长也真异想天开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.32,0:06:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,异想天开也得尝试
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说明了即将到来的战斗的残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.66,0:06:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下咋样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.98,0:06:51.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.17,0:06:52.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.69,0:06:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号的新战斗形态
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:06:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗形态…会变形吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.17,0:07:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么样还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这上面装的是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大功率光束武器 光子爆破炮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威力值超过了联邦军的现役主力兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超能米加粒子炮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.45,0:07:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就能对付UE的巨型舰了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可问题是 这么大规模的改造
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能在滞留期间内完成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有难度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.86,0:07:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 可以找他帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.37,0:07:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.16,0:07:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说巴明戈斯的宅邸就在对面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然住在这种森林里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.25,0:08:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 菲利特？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们先走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.38,0:08:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.41,0:08:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么关系 年轻人好奇心重
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚铃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.92,0:08:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.95,0:08:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.76,0:08:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 吓到你了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.53,0:08:30.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么…会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.31,0:08:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号在港内
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.03,0:08:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他肯定就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.32,0:08:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即前往逮捕古鲁迪克·艾诺亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.09,0:08:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:47.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.12,0:08:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这颗卫星胆敢阻挠联邦的介入 不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.06,0:08:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的宅子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:08:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,品味也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔扎克·巴明戈斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.74,0:09:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人称明斯利支配者的大富豪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.92,0:09:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风雅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.97,0:09:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古鲁迪克老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的事迹我听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.60,0:09:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是阿尔扎克·巴明戈斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.43,0:09:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃伊诺基的事实在让人伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:21.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我心目中 他是个杀也杀不死的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:25.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能够活着来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.82,0:09:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是因为他勇敢的举动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.93,0:09:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经决定倾尽全力协助你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:33.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃伊诺基也会就此瞑目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.77,0:09:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:40.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 他曾提到过一个颇有骨气的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.15,0:09:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是菲利特吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.47,0:09:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这座明斯利上被人收留了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.93,0:09:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收留…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:10:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的父母和弟弟都死于UE的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.17,0:10:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩我一个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被UE…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.41,0:10:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以一度住进了诺拉的某座收留所
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:15.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久后 有人说愿意领养我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做我的养父
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我当时无法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:24.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的家人 对我来说还…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.78,0:10:27.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就逃了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.84,0:10:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 遇到你驾驶着高达…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没遇到菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.77,0:10:35.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也和你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲母亲被UE…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以决心参加战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:46.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用妈妈留给我的高达
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.81,0:10:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还可以带着我驾驶高达吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.11,0:11:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在宇宙里 飘啊飘的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.83,0:11:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数着星座
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:07.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是卫星顶上映出的假星星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙里一定能看到更多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.84,0:11:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比谁找到的星星多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.75,0:11:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢星星？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着星星可以忘记许多事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:23.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 和菲利特在一起也很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:32.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.49,0:11:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的蝴蝶结
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还留着？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:37.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是我的护身符
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.43,0:11:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉战斗时能保护我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.53,0:11:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我希望它继续留在菲利特身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直保佑着菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.52,0:11:55.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的女儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.04,0:11:57.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是亲生的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:12:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要个女儿 收养的孤儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.14,0:12:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 她对我毫无感情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白费我一番苦心养育她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么才能让那孩子敞开心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为这事我整天苦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:17.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人称地球圈第一机动战士锻造师的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.85,0:12:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位麦德纳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.65,0:12:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况大致了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.63,0:12:25.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是一次鲁莽的大改造
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:28.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按一般方法做的话 怎么也来不及吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 这份工作就是专为不一般的我准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心 看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃尔夫也好 你也好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我身边尽是些提过分要求的客户
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.93,0:12:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没能在歌姬号内部发现古鲁迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说去见阿尔扎克·巴明戈斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.59,0:12:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 那我们也去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.49,0:12:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,监视歌姬号
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:55.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.65,0:13:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是菲利特吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.12,0:13:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃伊诺基向我提到过你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说就是你平息了法丁的内战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.20,0:13:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能说已经平息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:14.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是沃伊诺基先生和勒克特有那个意向
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.93,0:13:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的话语触动了那些思想陈旧的大人们的心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.09,0:13:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也许可以纠正这个世界的不公
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才答应参加
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.16,0:13:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场足以称之为鲁莽的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.06,0:13:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们想击败UE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,击败那些夺走人们心爱之人的UE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:33.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.19,0:13:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你的原动力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是过强的信念也可能致人走向毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.02,0:13:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心为好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.86,0:13:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 很高兴能和你谈话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴明戈斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请接纳柚铃成为家庭的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.44,0:13:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也许需要一些时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 柚铃更需要亲人！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.22,0:13:59.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.70,0:14:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少那也是我希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.33,0:14:07.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,专注于眼前的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:24.67,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}依偎彼此的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:34.99,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}愿这样的时光 永不结束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:46.64,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那样会有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:56.51,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}真心祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.76,0:15:07.97,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}寂寞时 回想起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.19,0:15:19.27,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,1000)}岁月的点点滴滴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.64,0:15:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚铃 明天是最后的日子了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.13,0:15:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天的作战会议结束后 我们就要出发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也见不到你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得有了朋友 又留下我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚铃 我会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:41.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗一结束就会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候还能见面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.51,0:15:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:46.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 向你保证
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.74,0:15:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚铃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.38,0:16:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于开始了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.83,0:16:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在空旷的森林里关了两个星期
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.51,0:16:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体都懒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是攻击目标 宇宙要塞安巴德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去曾是联邦军宇宙基地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因老化严重遭到遗弃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.60,0:16:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后就成了UE的巢穴？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.34,0:16:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,UE究竟是什么生物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.89,0:16:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题请稍后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始说明作战方案
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基于我们的兵力有限
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须保存实力 集中舰队炮火
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.64,0:16:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,截断敌人主力 形成推进
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.81,0:16:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机动战士编队
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.48,0:16:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在舰队炮火掩护下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登上要塞 直捣内部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用舰队打开突破口
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.05,0:16:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机动战士和敌人近身肉搏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:48.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那谁来给舰队护航？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.16,0:16:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰船会成为敌人机动战士的靶子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安排最低限度的兵力护航
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.64,0:16:56.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:16:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号的机动战士队
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就等你这句话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.22,0:17:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢您的协助
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.32,0:17:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就此告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚铃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:24.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚铃…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.88,0:17:26.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗结束后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.68,0:17:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会来找你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.20,0:17:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于能回船上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.64,0:17:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是宇宙里适合我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:41.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况不对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.35,0:17:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实能闻到 战斗的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.69,0:17:46.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.87,0:17:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦军？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:52.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.31,0:17:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叛逃者 古鲁迪克·艾诺亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即给我投降
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 乖乖别动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.77,0:18:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 上来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.99,0:18:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古鲁迪克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.74,0:18:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.87,0:18:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对UE的反击再不可能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.48,0:18:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.57,0:18:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.32,0:18:27.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方是联邦军…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易走到今天 就这么结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不放弃就还没有结束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让更多人有柚铃的遭遇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.46,0:18:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让UE为所欲为
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追上去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.41,0:18:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.10,0:18:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去救出古鲁迪克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:51.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在…说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟UE战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦军不做的话 我们去做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.00,0:19:00.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能摧毁宇宙要塞安巴德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.48,0:19:02.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦军说不定也会燃起斗志
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.96,0:19:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.96,0:19:06.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许能给一蹶不振的联邦军打上一剂强心针
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.01,0:19:08.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.35,0:19:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定了 跟着菲利特干！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.87,0:19:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 怎么做 菲利特？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.51,0:19:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用高达
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查了一下你的背景
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说想为家人报仇？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:26.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面对那些居心叵测的外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居心叵测的是联邦军
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.16,0:19:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦军隐瞒了UE的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.68,0:19:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 你到底知道些什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.55,0:19:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.63,0:19:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是来救古鲁迪克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不打算伤害你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:55.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.83,0:19:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 注意分寸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:20:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我开火
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己人之间内讧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.37,0:20:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,避免战斗扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.69,0:20:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:19.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会加害你 不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.56,0:20:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.06,0:20:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.18,0:20:41.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下定决心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.25,0:20:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别来碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.13,0:20:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰诺亚斯一眨眼就被…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.93,0:20:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中校 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发动引擎 不能把古鲁迪克交给他们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:21:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劝你们别轻举妄动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.85,0:21:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不也是联邦军吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:08.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦军里也要分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.34,0:21:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白人和不明白的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.03,0:21:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借我一用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.65,0:21:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得把通讯器材都交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.17,0:21:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法回头了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.04,0:21:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,营救叛逃者的你们也是叛逃者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.99,0:21:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗 无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.75,0:21:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够戏剧性
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.10,0:21:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.04,0:21:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不赶快的话 联邦会打歌姬号的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.78,0:21:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰队的准备完成了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.25,0:21:57.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 在外壁48号闸门回收我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.10,0:22:00.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙里照样可以抓他们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就得这样才有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.34,0:22:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.60,0:22:11.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外装看起来没什么区别啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.06,0:22:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 老头
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.42,0:22:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白这船的奥妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.78,0:22:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实战检验吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.63,0:22:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就快开始了
